    # his "Yeah. I didn't think about it like that, but Misha's right. Parties set a mood, and it would be a sad one. A sad party doesn't sound like a whole lot of fun."
    his "Sí. No lo pensé de esa manera, pero Misha tiene razón. Las fiestas fijan un estado de ánimo, y sería uno triste. Una fiesta triste no suena muy divertida."

# game/script-a4-shizune.rpy:3243
